data.description: Entertainer's dream home! Large open bonus room, screened porch and back deck overlooking a fenced back yard give many options for places to gather. Living room with vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace open to the dining room. Kitchen has built-ins with custom built cubby seating in breakfast area, white cabinets and pantry. Home is situated on the corner of a cul-de-sac and Richards Way Dr with a circular drive to make easy entry and exit. Primary bedroom has trey ceilings, walk-in closet and garden tub with separate shower. Laundry is located between kitchen and bonus room. This home offers ample space for what you need! HOA will be meeting in January for the year. Two outdoor storage buildings, one with electrical for workshop. Comes with the pool table!
